# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:12
translate chinese welch9_77b3956a:

    # "In Ms. Welch's class, I try to focus on my test, attempting to recall all the information that I had memorized while studying earlier in the week."
    "在韦尔奇老师的课堂上，我努力集中精力做试卷，试图回忆起本周早些时候复习时背下的所有知识。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:13
translate chinese welch9_1d38c971:

    # "Ms. Welch walks through the class, looking to see how everybody is doing and watching out for any cheaters."
    "韦尔奇老师在教室里巡视，观察大家的情况，同时警惕着是否有作弊者。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:16
translate chinese welch9_92d9ffe5:

    # "When she passes by my desk, she slides a small note down in front of me."
    "当她经过我的课桌时，她悄悄地将一张小纸条滑到我面前。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:17
translate chinese welch9_67c479b9:

    # "She does it so slyly, not even looking down as she places it, never missing a step as she continues walking the room."
    "她做得非常狡黠，放纸条时甚至没有低头，步伐丝毫未乱，继续在教室里巡视。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:18
translate chinese welch9_0e4d4622:

    # "I quietly unfold the note and take a look."
    "我悄悄地展开纸条看了一眼。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:25
translate chinese welch9_95ec0fac:

    # "I look up again and see her standing by her desk, smiling at me."
    "我再次抬头，看见她正站在自己的讲台旁，对我微笑。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:26
translate chinese welch9_00e23a96:

    # "She wants to talk to me. And gave me her phone number."
    "她想跟我聊聊。还给了我她的电话号码。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:27
translate chinese welch9_6bf4ecfb:

    # "I'll have to give her a call sometime soon, I guess."
    "我想我得找个时间给她打个电话了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:30
translate chinese welch9_af06cabf:

    # "Nothing else interesting happens the rest of the day, then I have to leave."
    "剩下的时间里没发生什么有趣的事，然后我就得走了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:33
translate chinese welch9_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "后来……"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:44
translate chinese welch9text1_36143372:

    # "My phone buzzes in my pocket. Looks like it's a text from Ms. Welch."
    "口袋里的手机震动起来。看来是韦尔奇老师发来的短信。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch9.rpy:55
translate chinese welch9text1_7cd60e3e:

